Getopt/ExPar version 1.00
=========================

Extended Parameters Command Line Arguments Parser

See POD for documentation.  Also look at t/1.t for examples.

This is a method-based, argumnt parsing and retrieving package.
Please send feedback to the author at harlinh@cadence.com for any issues.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

Currently no dependencies.

